\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 35. L. setaceum} Brot., {\i Phyt. Lusit.} 43 (1800). Like {\b 34} but leaves 0·5 mm wide, setaceous with inrolled margins, densely crowded in middle of stem; inflorescence lax, much-branched. 2n = 18. {\i S. Spain, C. & S. Portugal.} Hs Lu.
\par

